format.action:
RUNACTIONS(
  Image
    .FormulaMap(
      addrow(
        [Haiku/Drawings],
        Image,
        CurrentValue,
        Topic,
        Topic,
        Event,
        Event
      )
    ),
  thisRow.DeleteRows()
)

RunActions(
  ModifyRows(
    thisRow,
    [Categorization JSON],
    [OpenAI Vision]Vision(
      [Jon Dallas],
      parsejson(Image._merge() + "", "publicUrl"),
      "This image was a submission to our Haiku/Drawing contest for a community event exploring the arguments on all sides of " +
        Topic.ToText() +
        ". Help me categorize it. Respond in JSON with 4 keys: Transcription, Drawing Description, Haiku, and Analysis. 'Transcription' should be a verbatim transcription of any text in the image. If there is no text, leave this field blank. 'Drawing Description' should be a description of the drawing. If there is no drawing, leave this field blank. 'Analysis' should be a philosophical analysis of the image/haiku, exploring its meaning within the topic of" +
        Topic.ToText() +
        ", written concisely, punchy, directly, boldly, colloquially." +
        "'Valid Haiku' should be a boolean true or false value indicating whether the text is a valid Haiku (3 lines, 17 total syllables: 5, then 7, then 5). If there is no text, leave this field blank. Ensure all you writing is encoded for JSON.",
      200,"high","gpt-4-vision-preview"
    )
      .split(
        LineBreak()
      )
      .Filter(
        not(CurrentValue.left(3) = "```")
      )
      .Concatenate()
  ),
  ModifyRows(
    thisRow,
    [Text Transcription],
    [Categorization JSON].ParseJSON("Transcription"),
    [Drawing Description],
    [Categorization JSON].ParseJSON("Drawing Description"),
    [Valid Haiku],[Categorization JSON].ParseJSON("Haiku"),
    Analysis,[Categorization JSON].ParseJSON("Analysis")
  )
)
